import React from 'react'
import './Home.css'
import Navbar from '../Navbar/Navbar'
import Slide from './Slide'
import Product from '../Product/Product'
import Footer from '../Navbar/Footer'
const Home = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar/>
      <Slide/>
      <Product/>
      <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Home
